Bug ID: ANY-BUG-001
Title: Wallet funds not moving to "Holding Wallet" (Escrow) upon Invoice Acceptance.
Severity: Critical | Priority: High

Environment: Android 13, App Version 2.0.4, Staging Environment.

Steps to Reproduce:

Log in as Customer.

Accept an Invoice from a Vendor for 10,000.

Navigate to Wallet Screen.

Observe "Main Balance" and "Holding Wallet."

Actual Result: Main Balance is deducted, but Holding Wallet remains at 0.00. Funds are "lost" in the UI.

Expected Result: Main Balance should decrease by 10,000 and Holding Wallet should increase by 10,000.

[Network Log]: POST /api/v1/invoice/accept - 500 Internal Server Error (Database Deadlock)
